---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Uses"
  description="Hardware, software, and tools I use for development, photography, 3D printing, and home automation."
>
  <article class="prose max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Uses</h1>

    <p class="text-lg mb-8">
      A snapshot of the hardware, software, and tools I use daily. Inspired by{" "}
      <a href="https://uses.tech" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        uses.tech
      </a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Development</h2>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Editor & Terminal</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong>Cursor</strong> - VS Code fork with AI integration
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Claude Code</strong> - CLI AI coding assistant
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Warp</strong> - Modern terminal with AI features
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Fish shell</strong> - User-friendly shell with great defaults
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Languages & Frameworks</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong>TypeScript</strong> - Primary language for web projects
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>PHP</strong> - For backend work and LLM libraries
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Python</strong> - ML experiments and scripting
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Astro</strong> - Static sites (like this one)
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>React</strong> - Interactive components when needed
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Services</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong>Cloudflare</strong> - Pages, R2, DNS, CDN
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>GitHub</strong> - Code hosting and CI/CD
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Anthropic</strong> - Claude API for AI features
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Hardware</h2>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Desk Setup</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong>MacBook Pro</strong> - Primary development machine
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Apple Studio Display</strong> - 5K external monitor
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Apple Magic Keyboard</strong> - With Touch ID
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Apple Magic Trackpad</strong> - Gestures are essential
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">3D Printing</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong>Bambu Lab X1C</strong> - Fast, reliable enclosed printer
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Fusion 360</strong> - CAD for functional parts
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Bambu Studio</strong> - Slicer software
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Photography</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong>Sony A7 IV</strong> - Full-frame mirrorless
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Lightroom</strong> - Photo organization and editing
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Home Automation</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>
        <strong>Home Assistant</strong> - Central hub for automation
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Zigbee</strong> - Protocol for most sensors and switches
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>ESPHome</strong> - Custom ESP32-based sensors
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mt-8 text-[var(--color-text-muted)] italic">
      Last updated: January 2026
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
